"{\"uid\": \"albawaba.com-node-who-turkeys-famous-hitman-paris-olympics-1579681\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ALBAWABA - An athlete from Turkey who played for the country at the Paris Olympics went viral across social media because of his appearance as memes swarmed every platform with people calling him a \\\"Hitman\\\" and a \\\"trained assassin.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The individual in question is 51-year-old Yusuf Dikec of Turkey who wowed fans across social media for not having any specialized gear for shooting and appeared from the crown to give the sport a go.\", \"from\": 234, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_in_Islam\", \"score\": 0.9921991204332983, \"rank\": 0.007860698032235016, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_in_Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_in_Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 291, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To everyone's surprise, Dikec copped the silver medal!\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LadBible his appearance as \\\"This is what you call aura.\\\"\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Turkey sent a 51 yr old guy with no specialized lenses, eye cover or ear protection and got the silver medalpic.twitter.com/sFKcsRzvrw  He was wearing thick black glasses and a shirt with \\\"Turkey\\\" written on it to represent his beloved country at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 737, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"None of the special tools and equipment other contestants had like lenses and sound-dampening headphones.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One user on X (formerly known as Twitter) wrote, \\\"I love how everyone uses specialized lenses for shooting to avoid blur and increase precision...\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5199397801915395e-16, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then Turkey sends out a guy who looks like he just picked up the gun for fun and wins silver.\\\"\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, the 51-year-old also had his hands in his pockets for extra points while shooting to show comfort and capability.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was competing for Turkey for the 10m Air Pistol with partner Sevval Ilayda Tarhan and made history by copping the silver medal as mentioned above.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1318, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hillarious memes quickly swarmed social media because Turkey's Dikec put on quite a show for the audience there:    \\\"We can not change what's done, we can only move on.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9992285431548307, \"rank\": 0.0006542688726067305, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"https://t.co/Hwq582ExNEpic.twitter.com/4LPmqrMwuC  \\u00a9 2000 - 2025 Al Bawaba (www.albawaba.com)  Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive updates and enhanced content  Subscribe\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Bawaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Al Bawaba\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Bawaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Bawaba\"}]}]}"